11. Namio, 2006, “Senior Health-Care Residence Designing Premium Medical Assisted Living for the Elderly” Tokyo, Yasuo Hosokawa.
12. Regnier. V. A., 2003, “Assisted Living Housing for the Elderly：Design Innovations from the United States and Europe ”, New York, John Wiley & Sons, Inc.    

